text: Volkan Bozkır (born 22 November 1950) is a Turkish politician. He was the Minister of European Union Affairs from November 2015 to May 2016. He served as the President of the United Nations General Assembly from 2020 to 2021. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:Living people Category:Turkish politicians Category:Ambassadors of Turkey Category:Presidents of the United Nations General Assembly
